&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You’ll Be Doing:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As our Regional HR Manager in Xometry Türkiye, you’ll be responsible for running all aspects of the employee lifecycle – from hiring and onboarding to performance management and engagement – while ensuring compliance with Turkish labor law and collaborating with global HR teams.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
