&lt;li&gt;Ensure full compliance with Turkish labor law, SGK, and all legal HR obligations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Act as the single point of contact for employees and managers in Türkiye, providing day-to-day HR support and guidance.&lt;/li&gt;
